GSD.description:
clk: tegra: Fix refcount leak in tegra210_clock_init

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.150 by commit f487137a53b1a0692211f7ae82c0a7f87c30bdbe, it was introduced in version v4.5 by commit 6b301a059eb2ebed1b12a900e3b21a38e48dd410. For more details please see the references link.
